Dirt, originally from [[Hexen]], generalized by [[ZDoom]] to all games. However, sprites for this dirt aren't included in ZDoom.pk3, and must be provided. In Hexen.wad, the sprite is actually named ROCKF0 and is [[Sprite renaming|renamed at load-time]] by ZDoom.


